This is the usrp_ble-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the usrp_ble blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'usrp_ble', which is imported as:

    import usrp_ble

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(usrp_ble)
